p://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9999999863503036, \"rank\": 1.0261664588253895e-08, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 1823, \"end\": 1829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4722188250953738e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our room\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"our room\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"his four children\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar habit\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been fun.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just always when you are part of a team and you are not used to that everyone has different habits.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"different habits\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some of the guys prefer staying up late, some want to have a bit more of their own space, some are tidy, some are messy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"their own space\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray thinks that if anyone is the problem, it's him - \\\"I am tidy in comparison to my children but probably messy in comparison to most adults\\\" - al