even that early,\\\" he defends.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe the older lads should let Draper in on their \\\"Top Trumps\\\" style game where you have to name someone you have played against and guess their career-high ranking and whether they have been top 50 or not, with a points scale for correct answers.\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the older lads\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"Draper\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"Top Trumps\\\" style game\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"their career-high ranking\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3310}, {\"ngram\": \"a points scale\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3372}, {\"ngram\": \"correct answers\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even by tennis standards, it's pretty nerdy.\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tennis standards\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray, the ultimate tennis nerd, beats Evans and Skupski handily most nights.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3440, \"end\": 3446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4722188250953738e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3480, \"end\": 3485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999995913350102, \"rank\": 4.0866517395258017e-07, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ultimate t